description:
For over 33 years, the Church CO+OP has been helping churches, schools and nonprofits save time and money on products, services and education.

We connect nonprofit organizations with reputable vendors and resources to save time and money on products, services, and education.
How do we do it?
1) We screen prospective vendors;
2) we negotiate discounted rates with vendors;
3) secure vendor resources that bring value to our members;
4) connect our members with our vendors;
5) act as a liaison and advocate for members in times of need;
6) provide relevant educational opportunities at a reduced rate at the Texas Ministry Conference;
7) provide professional networking opportunities; and
8) provide tools to help you in your ministry and organization.
    9950 Cypresswood, Suite 320, Houston, Texas 77070, US
